long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get behind the wheel and experience the fast-paced life of a city cab driver in Taxi Simulator! Navigate through bustling streets, pick up passengers, and drive them to their destinations on time. Master the art of city driving, manage fuel, handle tricky traffic situations, and upgrade your taxi to earn more money. Explore dynamic environments, from downtown districts to suburban areas, while keeping your customers happy. Whether you're rushing through crowded streets or enjoying a leisurely ride, Taxi Simulator puts you in the driver's seat for the ultimate urban driving adventure!
